[SN]TITLE[SN]
Bristol firm to build 'world's biggest' hot air balloon

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The world's biggest ever hot air balloon is to be built in Bristol.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
8 October 2016 Last updated at 13:24 BST
It will be used to launch Russian Fedor Konyukhov into the stratosphere.
Cameron Balloons will build the balloon for the adventurer, who recently broke the round-the-world record.
